<p>dugouts etc for the night settling down about 9pm. I with Ern &amp; others used one of Fritz's 50 food Holes &amp; comfy were we on were stretchers, rough but springy &amp; easy.</p>
<p>21st. Wednesday.<br/>Breakfast 8.30am</p>
<p>Many Taubes up &amp; over us dropped few bombs without harm. Orders at 2 to move at 3pm. and set off after tea about 4pm. to sunken road trench in which we slept all night. relieving 6th Battn from</p>
